<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= title %></title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <div class="relative bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-500 to-teal-700 text-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16 md:py-24">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center">
        <div class="md:w-1/2 mb-8 md:mb-0">
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Baraka General Medical Clinic</h1>
          <p class="text-xl mb-8">Providing quality healthcare services with compassion and excellence.</p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
            <a href="/login" class="bg-white text-teal-700 hover:bg-gray-100 font-semibold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg shadow-md transition duration-300 text-center">
              Login
            </a>
            <a href="/register/patient" class="bg-teal-600 hover:bg-teal-700 border border-white font-semibold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg shadow-md transition duration-300 text-center">
              Register as Patient
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="md:w-1/2 flex justify-center">
          <div class="w-full max-w-md h-64 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-32 w-32 text-teal-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Wave Separator -->
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 1440 320" class="w-full h-auto">
        <path fill="#ffffff" fill-opacity="1" d="M0,96L48,112C96,128,192,160,288,160C384,160,480,128,576,122.7C672,117,768,139,864,149.3C960,160,1056,160,1152,138.7C1248,117,1344,75,1392,53.3L1440,32L1440,320L1392,320C1344,320,1248,320,1152,320C1056,320,960,320,864,320C768,320,672,320,576,320C480,320,384,320,288,320C192,320,96,320,48,320L0,320Z"></path>
      </svg>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Features Section -->
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12 text-gray-800">Our Services</h2>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Feature 1 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition duration-300">
        <div class="rounded-full bg-teal-100 w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-teal-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-800">Patient Registration</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Easy and secure registration process for new patients with access to personal health records.</p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Feature 2 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition duration-300">
        <div class="rounded-full bg-teal-100 w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-teal-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-800">Doctor Assignment</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Efficient assignment of doctors to patients based on specialization and availability.</p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Feature 3 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition duration-300">
        <div class="rounded-full bg-teal-100 w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-teal-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 9V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2m2 4h10a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H9a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm7-5a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-800">Billing Management</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Transparent and organized billing system for all medical services provided.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- About Section -->
  <div class="bg-gray-100 py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center">
        <div class="md:w-1/2 mb-8 md:mb-0">
          <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-md max-w-md mx-auto">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-full w-full text-teal-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4" />
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-800">About Our Clinic</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Baraka General Medical Clinic is dedicated to providing high-quality healthcare services to our community. Our team of experienced medical professionals is committed to delivering personalized care with compassion and excellence.</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">We utilize modern technology to streamline our operations and enhance the patient experience, ensuring that you receive the best possible care in a comfortable and efficient environment.</p>
          <a href="/login" class="inline-block bg-teal-600 hover:bg-teal-700 text-white font-semibold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg shadow-md transition duration-300">
            Get Started
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="bg-gray-800 text-white py-8">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between">
        <div class="mb-6 md:mb-0">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Baraka General Medical Clinic</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400">Providing quality healthcare services</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mb-6 md:mb-0">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-4">Quick Links</h4>
          <ul class="space-y-2">
            <li><a href="/" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition duration-300">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="/login" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition duration-300">Login</a></li>
            <li><a href="/register/patient" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition duration-300">Register</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-4">Contact Us</h4>
          <address class="text-gray-400 not-italic">
            <p>123 Medical Plaza</p>
            <p>Nairobi, Kenya</p>
            <p class="mt-2">Email: info@barakaclinic.com</p>
            <p>Phone: +254 700 000 000</p>
          </address>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="border-t border-gray-700 mt-8 pt-6 text-center text-gray-400">
        <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Baraka General Medical Clinic. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
